text: Copdock and Washbrook is a civil parish in Babergh, Suffolk, England. In 2011, there were 1,114 people living in Copdock and Washbrook. It has the villages of Copdock and Washbrook, and has the hamlets of Coles Green, Mace Green and Washbrook Street. == References == Category:Civil parishes in Suffolk Category:Settlements in Babergh
